** Your opportunity: **

We have an exciting, permanent full-time opportunity for a ** GIS Product
Engineer ** to join our Product Asset Intelligence team within our Digital and
Information group.

The GIS Product Engineer supports the Spatial Product Manager delivering the
Spatial product roadmap as well as providing ongoing operational support of
the enterprise spatial solution for Urban Utilities.

Primarily a team facing role collaborating with the Product and Business leads
to deliver Spatial continuous improvement and project deliverables. You will
be responsible for the design, development, and delivery of scalable and
automated Spatial solutions. Provide ITIL level 2 support for the enterprise
GIS solution which includes ESRI Enterprise GIS, AGOL and Portal, FME,
Microsoft SQL database and Geocortex. Customer support and engagement
activities to ensure Urban Utilities attains the maximum benefits from the
Spatial Product.

You’ll find more details in the position description here [ DI-GIS Product
Engineer-E2570.1-20220224.pdf ](https://secure.dc2.pageuppeople.com/apply/Tran
